{"tid":1493252,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"獨立調查委員會會成立, 但內容唔會係我地要既野, 然後整個活動會完","createTime":"2019-08-21T07:24:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T08:12:57.000Z","uid":221856,"like":93,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"fe558ce9f30a3c71e90b5cd8c619769605c0165b","tid":1493252,"uid":221856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T07:24:55.000Z","msg":"劇本:<br />\n由政府口風軟化, 同埋監警會主席放風可以預測到 <strong>獨立調查委員會會成立</strong><br />\n但<span style=\"font-size: large;\">內容一定唔係搵獨立(e.g 退休法官) 之類, 會是但搵啲假中立人士去做</span><br />\n而<span style=\"font-size: large;\">調查方向亦會好似監警會主席放風咁, 係講點樣改善警隊</span><br />\n之後建制同藍絲就會瘋狂攻擊 成立左啦 又唔滿意, 想點撚樣呀<br />\nSpin完, 最後另外4個訴求不了了之<br />\n我地亦重回佔中既失敗<br />\n<br />\n認同既幫手推下吧<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">建議:</span><br />\n文宣要開始多講獨立調查委員會會 具體內容<br />\n目的係要民間有共識, 點先係真正獨立, 同埋調查方向唔係改善警隊, 而係搵出錯源頭, 劍唔一定指警隊, 絕對可以係政府決策官員<br />\n唔可以比佢又出袋住先, spin走民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09423754926565b492a640a32f497e241022a849","tid":1493252,"uid":281926,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T07:25:59.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守！智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It&rsquo;s now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uvSwHez.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuvSwHez.png&h=660b03dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f7a432e6edd142a322708991bd1553af25c07f0","tid":1493252,"uid":44461,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T07:35:05.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"84261fb0dd6ad947c3a8423e473641306ddeff7f","tid":1493252,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T07:40:42.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.g